---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Memory Systems Group</h1>
		
		<div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600">
			<p class="mb-6">
				The Memory Systems Group was founded with a singular vision: to bridge the gap between biological understanding and artificial implementation of memory.
			</p>
			
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
			<p class="mb-6">
				Memory is the foundation of identity, learning, and culture. By studying memory across different substrates—neurons, silicon, and society—we aim to uncover universal principles that can lead to better AI, treatments for memory disorders, and more resilient information systems.
			</p>

			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">What We Do</h2>
			<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
				<li>Conduct interdisciplinary research combining neuroscience, computer science, and psychology.</li>
				<li>Develop open-source tools for memory research and analysis.</li>
				<li>Host workshops and seminars to foster collaboration.</li>
				<li>Publish findings in top-tier journals and conferences.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Join Our Community</h2>
			<p>
				We are always looking for passionate individuals to join our cause. Whether you are a student, a seasoned researcher, or just curious, there is a place for you here.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
